Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.92,0:01:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭  這次又是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.86,0:01:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這邊了  快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.12,0:01:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我  戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.26,0:01:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Trick  or  Treat
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.63,0:01:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.27,0:01:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.83,0:03:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.13,0:03:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的早飯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.14,0:03:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  阿春
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.74,0:03:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎  撿到遺失物的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.03,0:03:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能從中取得20%作為報酬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.19,0:03:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.72,0:03:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我給5%
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.84,0:04:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你這種小氣鬼就要懲罰20%
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.53,0:04:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.50,0:04:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑雪公主學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.72,0:04:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大清早的就玩得那麼愉快  真好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.13,0:04:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.26,0:04:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我錯了  以後不敢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.14,0:04:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.01,0:04:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿春  我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.68,0:04:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  今天到我值日
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.53,0:04:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.33,0:04:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry?  K
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.99,0:04:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送你去學校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.67,0:04:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pard？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.87,0:04:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  阿春
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.21,0:04:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  總是讓女人救
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.27,0:04:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼突然來這邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.65,0:04:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤之王有話傳給黑之王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.42,0:04:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心區域網鬧事份子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.38,0:04:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要對我說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.51,0:05:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不直接跟她說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.83,0:05:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能更有趣一些？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.37,0:05:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是疑問語氣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.03,0:05:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NP
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是沒問題  問題可大了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.70,0:05:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通知集合的郵件上只寫著有要事幾個字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.18,0:05:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐肯定是生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.91,0:05:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴安  有田
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.67,0:05:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.27,0:05:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經聽公主說過了  你不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.56,0:05:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是要商量些什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.60,0:05:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思  你不用招呼我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.23,0:05:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有田很喜歡對人道歉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.14,0:05:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.19,0:06:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是不得不道歉的情況比較多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就我而言…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.52,0:06:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  公主似乎從早上起心情就不是太好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.79,0:06:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麼頭緒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.84,0:06:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭緒…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.98,0:06:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我這種人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.03,0:06:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑雪公主學姐怎麼會因為我而不高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.20,0:06:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有田總是叫公主做學姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是當然的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.68,0:06:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實說  我稍微有點妒忌你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.41,0:06:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為一直以來  和公主直連以及一起上學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.66,0:06:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我的特權
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.29,0:06:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你出現之後就變了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.61,0:06:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你誤會了  若宮學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.17,0:06:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和黑雪公主學姐的關係  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.82,0:06:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說的話就是利害一致
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.44,0:06:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像弟子和老師那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.27,0:07:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概沒有私人感情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.28,0:07:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是一點私人感情都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.27,0:07:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  我們遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.72,0:07:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事去了老師辦公室一趟…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.63,0:07:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.32,0:07:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你們叫來不為別的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.94,0:07:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有事想拜託你們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.45,0:07:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實最近在校園區域網內發生了某起事件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.89,0:07:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們有聽說什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.61,0:07:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…阿千呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.48,0:07:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  仁子有話讓我轉達
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.20,0:07:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內容是小心區域網鬧事份子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.05,0:07:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧  阿春  你和赤之王一直保持聯絡？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.04,0:08:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  剛才Pard讓我轉達的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  還坐到人家摩托車的後座了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.81,0:08:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那樣沒錯  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.03,0:08:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報告完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.10,0:08:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等會我再問問她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.08,0:08:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定除了梅鄉中學以外也有事發生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.26,0:08:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以外的意思是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.82,0:08:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  有學生在放學後被留在了校園區域網
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.35,0:08:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(215,328)}Avatar
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.35,0:08:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虛擬角色的衣服和物品都被人扒光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.04,0:08:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿盔甲和拿槍的南瓜頭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.04,0:08:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  還攻破了禁止過分接觸的系統限制
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.14,0:08:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是學姐  為什麼要和我們說這事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.90,0:08:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理由有三個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.65,0:08:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先  對方好像使用了系統外的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.91,0:08:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果屬實的話  僅靠學生會成員恐怕應付不來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.11,0:09:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其次  如果事情鬧大了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.83,0:09:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能引來有關部門的干預
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.64,0:09:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令當前學生會的權限受到限制
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.03,0:09:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想盡可能地避免這個事態
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.06,0:09:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟有可能再次發生像能美那樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.34,0:09:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後第三  我最信賴的就是你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.96,0:09:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虛擬角色搶劫絕對不能原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.13,0:09:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會盡力幫忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.56,0:09:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當然也會幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.52,0:09:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿春…也不用問了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.60,0:09:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是遵循學姐的指令
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.69,0:09:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間定在放學之後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.33,0:09:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你們了  拓武  千百合
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.22,0:09:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.72,0:10:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生虛擬角色搶劫的果然不僅我們學校嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.15,0:10:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  但從收集到的情報來看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.28,0:10:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得有點不對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.66,0:10:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕而易舉地入侵防禦堅固的學校網路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不留一點痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.79,0:10:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就駭客來說可是個高手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.42,0:10:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但做的僅僅是扒光虛擬角色的衣服和物品
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.28,0:10:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手法和目的之間不對等  反而令人覺得可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.77,0:10:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之這次就是我多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.17,0:10:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了  感謝你提供情報
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.71,0:10:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這人情你要我怎麼還
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.95,0:10:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想  那就把Silver  Crow讓給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.84,0:10:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了  我會考慮的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.51,0:10:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  他可能在你那邊才有更好的發展
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.97,0:10:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  黑色的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:11:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑  給我忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.21,0:11:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這女人  到底是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.73,0:11:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上月同學  方便的話能幫忙搬一下教材嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.78,0:11:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  老師  我很樂意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.30,0:11:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅鄉中學校園區域網統一下線時間快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.56,0:11:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請對文件進行保存  退出連線
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.38,0:11:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重複一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.54,0:11:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他會來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.88,0:11:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就不清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.44,0:11:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那個  阿春你今天真安靜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.43,0:11:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從早上起  就讓她看到很多出糗的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.26,0:11:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是乎黑雪公主學姐好像生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.75,0:11:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生氣了？  我看上去不像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.06,0:11:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像…是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.93,0:11:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊  再說我瞭解女人心的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.95,0:11:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不會吃那麼多苦頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.51,0:11:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.08,0:11:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說啊  女孩子真是莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.29,0:12:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千百合  唐突地問一句
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.04,0:12:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.07,0:12:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我待人的態度很強硬嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.54,0:12:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會令人很緊張嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.93,0:12:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼…？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.38,0:12:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春雪在我面前總是畏畏縮縮的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.35,0:12:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看著也覺得痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.55,0:12:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐確實說不上很容易相處
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.94,0:12:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.08,0:12:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  果然是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.17,0:12:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還是阿雪的問題更嚴重些
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.40,0:12:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.75,0:12:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.68,0:12:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Trick  or  Treat
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.59,0:13:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按計劃行事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.81,0:13:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.44,0:13:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿拓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.85,0:13:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上鉤了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.02,0:13:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎你哦  南瓜燈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.94,0:13:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.66,0:13:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止了  你這個大南瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.23,0:13:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.30,0:13:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.73,0:13:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.67,0:13:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎能在FPS領域裡認輸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.09,0:13:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.06,0:14:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳送門開啟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.29,0:14:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  身體好輕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.74,0:14:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  阿拓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.66,0:14:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼  阿千你沒事就好…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.67,0:14:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.91,0:14:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來這個空間重力很小
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.67,0:14:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這裡到底是哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.43,0:14:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡應該不是校園區域網吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.91,0:14:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿千你快點起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.38,0:14:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  你想說我很重嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.21,0:14:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到Accel  Assault
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.19,0:14:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.32,0:15:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫DShK
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.58,0:15:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(359,328)}Assault  Linker
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.57,0:15:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後一名火力連線者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.96,0:15:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火力連線者？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.93,0:15:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於找到你了  我的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.93,0:15:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(320,328)}Assault  Link
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.94,0:15:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火力連線
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.45,0:15:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二回合
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.14,0:15:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.37,0:15:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.92,0:15:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿千
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.71,0:15:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿千
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.67,0:15:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時鐘停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.49,0:15:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.46,0:16:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.92,0:16:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們  快想像自己的虛擬角色
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.90,0:16:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後高呼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.66,0:16:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(320,328)}Burst  Link
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.66,0:16:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超頻連線
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.24,0:16:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐好美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.97,0:16:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.91,0:16:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是加速世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.82,0:16:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然和Brain  Burst不太一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.89,0:16:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這個空間也由類似的法則支配
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.84,0:16:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.94,0:16:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超頻連線
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.36,0:16:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我們也來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.20,0:16:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.20,0:16:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超頻連線
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.79,0:17:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪你們精神不夠集中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.25,0:17:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(346,328)}Elemental  Bullet
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.24,0:17:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召喚  元素子彈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.05,0:17:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數量太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.52,0:17:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿千  快用我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.72,0:17:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.41,0:17:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.47,0:17:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.27,0:17:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(301,328)}Lightning
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.29,0:17:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷霆——
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.08,0:17:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿千  剛開始就用必殺？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.44,0:17:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(340,328)}Cyan  Spike
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.46,0:17:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,——快槍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.15,0:17:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暢快！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.65,0:17:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  接著去攻擊本體
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.92,0:17:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我們也去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.96,0:17:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.88,0:17:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(320,328)}Cyan  Spike
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.88,0:17:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快槍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:17:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(320,328)}Cyan  Spike
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:17:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快槍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.68,0:17:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(320,328)}Cyan  Spike
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.68,0:17:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快槍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.51,0:18:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一定可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.17,0:18:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.61,0:18:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別太得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.04,0:18:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(320,328)}Splash  Stinger
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.03,0:18:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛針四射
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.09,0:18:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太浪費彈藥了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.82,0:18:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.57,0:18:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(320,328)}Splash  Stinger
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.56,0:18:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛針四射
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.58,0:19:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿千…彈藥…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.42,0:19:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒彈藥了  讓我休息下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.25,0:19:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼呀  真沒用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.50,0:19:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿春你也怎麼了  老發呆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.31,0:19:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.45,0:19:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的盤旋速度並不是很快
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.50,0:19:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用機動力決一勝負的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.76,0:19:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快告訴軍團長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.70,0:19:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…就這種程度學姐應該早就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.18,0:19:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不著我特意去告訴她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.59,0:19:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且只是知道而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.13,0:19:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是有什麼應對的方法…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.14,0:19:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別磨磨蹭蹭的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.64,0:19:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點去學姐那裡  阿春
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.80,0:19:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐始終是個女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.81,0:19:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾也希望有男孩子能幫助自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.50,0:19:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主動地和自己說話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.61,0:19:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你這麼說  我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.71,0:19:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿千  左邊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.89,0:19:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想跑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.05,0:19:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿千  在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.03,0:19:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.67,0:19:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.64,0:20:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是學姐也能在空中自由移動的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.49,0:20:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去  阿春
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.53,0:20:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然我再也不讓你吃我媽媽做的飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.86,0:20:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.86,0:20:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿千  阿拓  謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.97,0:20:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春雪？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.74,0:20:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅靠物理攻擊力是打不贏她的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.99,0:20:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要看清她移動的破綻  迅速展開攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.40,0:20:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換言之  要瞄準她盤旋的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.42,0:20:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.00,0:20:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過要怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.55,0:20:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是低重力空間
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.16,0:20:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在空中可是對她有利
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.21,0:20:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來成為學姐的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.71,0:20:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…學姐請專注物理攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.71,0:20:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.52,0:20:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.01,0:20:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你終於肯當面和我說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.73,0:20:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼小的翅膀可能幫不上你的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.19,0:21:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個空間和Brain  Burst一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.21,0:21:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想像力——心念在這裡也能發揮效用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.21,0:21:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由此想像將會成為你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.50,0:21:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你渴望的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.51,0:21:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所渴望的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.12,0:21:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是——
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.54,0:21:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我和學姐一起翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.46,0:21:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧  學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.34,0:21:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.97,0:21:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.33,0:21:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.13,0:21:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用自己的翅膀翱翔  原來是那麼暢快的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.62,0:21:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.98,0:22:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.31,0:22:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都能結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.25,0:22:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍團長  這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.65,0:22:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空間正在崩潰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.49,0:22:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.83,0:22:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是傳送門
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.09,0:22:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.42,0:23:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿千  到極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.35,0:23:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經沒油了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.86,0:23:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  再加一把勁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.36,0:23:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真會使喚人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.55,0:23:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.92,0:23:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.09,0:23:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼  我在想她的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.75,0:23:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DShK她…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.53,0:23:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人覺得有點傷感
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.81,0:23:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不再有人登陸的伺服器裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.97,0:23:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待著對戰對手出現
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.59,0:23:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後就像喪失人氣的遊戲終止運營一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.96,0:23:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎  在我打倒她的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.02,0:24:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種遊戲通關之後  帶著不捨的滿足感
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.72,0:24:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她當時一定也是這種心情
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.89,0:24:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.44,0:24:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.23,0:24:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  春雪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.88,0:24:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後合體的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.25,0:24:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看你好像想挑戰什麼  可是隨後又放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.57,0:24:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.09,0:24:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  那只是一時情急
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.39,0:24:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者說是考驗下我的膽量…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.79,0:24:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  等我有一天有了那份自信之後
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.66,0:24:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請允許我直接叫你…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.89,0:24:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫學姐你的真名
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.36,0:24:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  在那之前我都是黑雪公主
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.44,0:24:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
